# Input file for DRIFTORBIT - Version 1.1
# 
#
1d-5		    M_t		       - Mach number (for single Mach no. run)
1d19		    n0		       - particle density
2.255607593E+04     vth		       - thermal velocity
1		    epsmn	       - perturbation amplitude B1/B0
0		    m		       - poroidal perturbation mode
3 		    n		       - toroidal perturbation mode (MUST BE > 0)
0		    mth		       - poloidal canonical mode (for single Mach no. run)
10		    mthnum	       - poloidal canonical mode count
1d-5		    Mtmin	       - minimum Mach number
0.1		    Mtmax	       - maximum Mach number
30                  Mtnum              - Mach number count
F		    nobdrift	       - neglect magnetic drift (drift-orbit resonances)
T		    nopassing	       - neglect passing particles
F		    calcflux	       - calculate flux directly instead via flux-force relation
F		    noshear	       - neglect magnetic shear term with dqds
